data.description: Isar 是一款专门为 Flutter 打造的支持全文检索、ACID 语义、类型静态的高可扩展性、异步多线程超高速、跨平台开源数据库。

data.label: Isar Database
data.description: Isar is a highly scalable, asynchronous, multi-threaded, ultra-fast, cross-platform open-source database with full-text search, ACID semantics, and static typing, specifically built for Flutter.
